videos.description: Jordan Bowden gets the steal and passes to Jordan Bone who he kicks it back to Bowden for the transition 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bowden turns defense into offense

videos.description: Jordan Bowden comes off the screen and knocks down the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Volunteers' Bowden has the hot hand

videos.description: Larry Austin Jr. makes a no-look dish to Clevon Brown who throws down the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Austin-Brown connection leads to nice play

videos.description: Riley Lachance dribbles, spins around, and knocks down the nice jumper.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Lachance putting the moves on defender

videos.description: Lamonte Turner knocks down the 3-point jumper then Jordan Bowden makes the transition layup to push Tennessee past Vanderbilt 67-62.
videos.headline: Volunteers go on a 5-0 run to seal the game
